Definition: the military doctrine that an enemy will be deterred from using nuclear weapons as long as he can be destroyed as a consequence
Example: when two nations both resort to nuclear deterrence the consequence could be mutual destruction
Synonyms: deterrence, noun, cognition, doctrine, group, military, c, the, that, an, enemy, will, be, deterred, from, using, nuclear, weapons, as, long, he, can, destroyed, a, consequence, when, two, nations, both, resort, to, could, mutual, destruction
Category: noun.act
